WW3.<br><br>And can someone explain what North Korea has been doing recently to get Bush all hot under the collar? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unenabierdieb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nena Bierdieb</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/1/02 10:03:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseranthallgripeswishes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4495.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: &quot;Axis of Evil&quot;</span><hr size=1> I think he's suggesting that weapons of mass destruction in the hands of zealots is evil.  If it was anti-democracy or anti-capitalism that list would be a lot longer, don't you think?<br><br>And to answer your last question:<br><!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> North Korea is a regime arming with missiles and weapons of mass destruction, while starving its citizens. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>It was in the address long before &quot;Axis of Evil&quot; was mentioned to sum it all up.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucaowyth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caowyth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/1/02 10:32:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseranthallgripeswishes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4495.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: &quot;Axis of Evil&quot;</span><hr size=1> I think the world would be better off without those three countries, but at the same time he is pushing things quite a bit. He needs to back off the rhetoric a bit.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcol