angent and take out targets that have been chafing the US for a while. I unfortunatly see this &quot;War of Terrorism&quot; changing into a cover up for an econemy in recession, and &quot;Reganomics&quot; all over again. I also feel for the most part that George Bush Jr is a puppet, being worked by his father to continue the fights that George Bush Sr. began a while ago. Faith in the goverment actualy doing what is in the best intrest of the world is failing me. Too many times they jump on the oppertunity to do what they want under the guise of helping everyone. Only time will tell. <p>Graynd Theftauto <BR>"The other dead meat" <BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uyalum.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yalum</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/1/02 3:12:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseranthallgripeswishes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4495.topic&index=15>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: One billion dollars!</span><hr size=1> Come on, guys, it took more than a decade for the Republicans to find a replacement to the Soviets, let them have a little fun with it.  It's not like the military types mind being ordered to go blow stuff up.<br><br>Although why Ashcroft decided we had to start all over agin with McCarthyism is beyond me... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulisboa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lisboa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/1/02 3:25:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseranthallgripeswishes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4495.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: One billion dollars!</span><hr size=1> Action is good.  But action against the wrong target is bad.  I feel like something is going to happen with Pakistan, and I believe they did provide dialysis treatment for Bin Laden--if he's alive, he probably is there right now.  Other places to consider action would be Chechnya, Somalia, the Philipenes, and Indonesia, these are the nations that currently have the terrorist training camps (granted, the Philipenes is opposed to terrorism, but they're getting destablized).  <br><br>Iraq is always a convenient target, but Saddam has never been a religious zealot--it's not the right target right now.  Naming Iran and North Korea is totally random.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukoru.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Koru</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/1/02 3:52:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseranthallgripeswishes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4495.topic&index=17>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: One billion dollars!</span><hr size=1> The &quot;Axis of evil&quot; phrase is unfortunate at best. Yeah, they're bad bad nations. We can get the drift without making catchy sounding allusions to WW2. As for Iraq, great. About time the unfinished job there got 